    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3131500051" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9778481987275779728">This is a hard book for me to rate and review. <br/><br/>I could listen to David Foster Wallace talk all day but his writing is just hard. It requires work, which isn’t necessarily a bad thing. <br/><br/>Although short and relatively simple I adored the first short story ‘A radically condensed history of postindustrial life’ and struggled with the more complex titles such as ‘Tri-stan: I Sold Sisee Nar To Ecko’</span>

